en selector\">.Hoge</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 480px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.Hoge</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}